This paper is likely to belong to the Game Theory (cs.GT) category because it deals with strategy sets and rationality in decision-making. It could also be classified under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) because it involves modeling rational behavior. Additionally, it could be categorized under Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) because it deals with refining strategies, and Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA) because it involves multiple players.
